{
  "id": "douyin-video",
  "platform": "douyin",
  "mode": "video",
  "name": "抖音 · 视频",
  "options": [
    {
      "id": "aspect",
      "default": "9:16",
      "aspects": [
        "9:16",
        "3:4",
        "1:1",
        "16:9"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "titleMaxLen",
      "label": "标题字数上限",
      "type": "number",
      "default": "55",
      "min": 8,
      "max": 80
    },
    {
      "id": "contentLen",
      "label": "正文/脚本字数",
      "type": "number",
      "default": "300",
      "min": 80,
      "max": 4000,
      "step": 50
    }
  ],
  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "title",
      "name": "标题生成",
      "type": "title",
      "needs": [],
      "promptTemplate": "douyin/video/title.md",
      "humanGate": true,
      "defaultProvider": "cli-claude"
    },
    {
      "id": "content",
      "name": "口播稿生成",
      "type": "content",
      "needs": [
        "title"
      ],
      "promptTemplate": "douyin/video/content.md",
      "defaultProvider": "cli-claude"
    },
    {
      "use": "cover",
      "promptTemplate": "douyin/video/cover.md",
      "aspects": [
        "9:16",
        "3:4",
        "1:1",
        "16:9"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "video",
      "name": "分镜与剪映草稿",
      "type": "video",
      "needs": [
        "content"
      ],
      "promptTemplate": "douyin/video/storyboard.md",
      "defaultProvider": "cli-gemini",
      "post": "jianying-draft"
    },
    "review"
  ],
  "notes": [
    "视频前 3 秒必须出现核心钩子，否则完播率会显著下降",
    "标题不超过 55 字，话题标签 3-5 个，避免堆砌",
    "封面使用 9:16 竖版（1080x1920），文字占比不超过 1/3",
    "不要在视频或文案中出现外链、二维码、微信号",
    "发布时间建议：工作日 12:00-13:00 / 18:00-21:00",
    "发布前确认无极限词（最/第一/国家级等）"
  ]
}
